item.title: Deltascape client not connecting to server ip
item.dc:creator: @CoonHunter CoonHunter
item.description:
@CoonHunter wrote:

If it connects fine to 127.0.0.1 there is nothing wrong with the client, just either:
A > You lack the knowledge to properly change the IP (Obviously you do or it would still be connecting via localhost)
B > You either didn’t port forward at all, or at least not correctly.
C > You are using a NO-IP address incorrectly.
